  The $[m-n]$ itself is an index with elements  

\begin{align*}
  [0-n] &: [0, -1, -2,\ldots, -(N-1)] \\
  [1-n] &: [1, 0, -1, \ldots, 1-(N-1)] \\
  \vdots\quad & \\
  [m-n] &: [m, m-1, m-2, \ldots, m-n, \ldots, m-(N-1)] \\
  \vdots\quad & \\
  [(N-1)-n] &: [(N-1), (N-1)-1, (N-1)-2, \ldots, 0]
\end{align*}
  
  The question remains, what does $f[-n]$, and by extension $f[m-n]$, look like?
