  &= \sum_{n=0}^{N/d-1} \bigl(e^{-i2\pi k d / N}\bigr)^n \\
\intertext{For $kd=0 \text{ mod } N$, and for $k=0 \text{ mod } N/d$, for ie: $k=0, N/d, 2N/d, 3N/d,\ldots \in [0:N-1]$}
