  It is easier to disect the sum with the factor of $N$ on the other side
  $$N F_k = {1\over 2} \biggl(\omega_N^{-kN/4} + \omega_N^{kN/4}\biggr) + \sum_{n=-N/4+1}^{N/4-1} \omega_N^{-kn}$$
