  fixing the frequency $s$, then it is periodic with period $1/s$
  $$e^{2\pi is (t + {1\over s})}$$
  $$= e^{2\pi ist} e^{2\pi is {1\over s}}$$
  $$= e^{2\pi ist}$$
  will be equal to 1 at the points $t = 0, \pm {1\over s}, \pm {2\over s},\ldots$ spaced $1\over s$ apart.
  
